'''爱国者公园'''是[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[莫斯科州|莫斯科州]][[奥金佐沃区|奥金佐沃区]][[库宾卡|库宾卡]]的一个主题公园，围绕军事装备主题设计，包括军事装备的互动展览<ref name=Walker>{{cite news|last1=Walker|first1=Shaun|title=Vladimir Putin opens Russian 'military Disneyland' Patriot Park|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/16/vladimir-putin-opens-russian-military-disneyland-patriot-park|accessdate=22 June 2015|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=16 June 2015|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215162101/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/16/vladimir-putin-opens-russian-military-disneyland-patriot-park|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=FeldmanMiller>{{cite news|last1=Feldman|first1=Evgeny|last2=Miller|first2=Christopher|title=Patriot Park: Russia's 'military Disneyland' is fun for the whole warmongering family|url=http://mashable.com/2015/06/19/russia-military-disneyland/|accessdate=22 June 2015|publisher=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|date=20 June 2015|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205133644/https://mashable.com/2015/06/19/russia-military-disneyland/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Plucinska>{{cite news|last1=Plucinska|first1=Joanna|title=Russia Just Opened a Theme Park for Warmongers|url=http://time.com/3923842/putin-kubinka-moscow-patriot-park-russia-opens-a-military-playground-for-the-patriotic/|accessdate=22 June 2015|publisher=[[TIME|TIME]]|date=17 June 2015|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411001341/https://time.com/3923842/putin-kubinka-moscow-patriot-park-russia-opens-a-military-playground-for-the-patriotic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。公园于2016年正式开放，<ref>{{cite web|title=The Russian military is building a mini-Reichstag at its amusement park so that kids have 'a real building to storm'|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/02/22/the-russian-military-is-building-a-mini-reichstag-at-its-amusement-park-so-that-kids-have-a-real-building-to-storm/|website=Washington Post|accessdate=9 March 2017|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209143827/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/02/22/the-russian-military-is-building-a-mini-reichstag-at-its-amusement-park-so-that-kids-have-a-real-building-to-storm/|dead-url=no}}</ref>  

公园内包括库宾卡空军基地的航空博物馆，和[[库宾卡坦克博物馆|库宾卡坦克博物馆]]。自2015年以来，公园主办国际军事技术论坛。2020年，[[俄罗斯武装力量主教座堂|俄罗斯武装力量主教座堂]]在公园内建成。展品的位置和对平民参观者的限制经常在没有任何通知的情况下改变。

* 土地总面积 — 5,414 公顷<ref name = "LCR">{{Cite web |url=http://park-patriot.ru/23/ |title=Laying ceremony report (9 June 2014) |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2018-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919211626/http://park-patriot.ru/23/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
* 军事基地 — 3，530公顷<ref name = "LCR"/>
* 民用部分 — 1，884公顷<ref name = "LCR"/>
* 参观人数最多为20，000人<ref name = "LCR"/>

爱国者公园内的射击场面积超过160公顷<ref name = "LCR"/><ref name = "TFB1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2016/12/13/patriot-park-extreme-shooting-range-world-shoot-russia-2017/ |title=Patriot Park - The Extreme Shooting Range of World Shoot Russia 2017 - The Firearm Blog |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119192020/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2016/12/13/patriot-park-extreme-shooting-range-world-shoot-russia-2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，整个射击场宽2，500多米，<ref name = "TFB1"/>。总容量超过2，000人。<ref name = "TFB1"/>

